{"tid":1589553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"財務和理非唔該入一入嚟，有關黨鐵","createTime":"2019-09-23T10:40:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T11:27:09.000Z","uid":53702,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"7aa027a8ca68e835c5796f5be757cf5479843fa5","tid":1589553,"uid":53702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:40:47.000Z","msg":"大家呢排爆黨鐵，其實風險都好大，對於黨鐵其實又不痛不癢，有冇諗過一啲令管理層痛嘅方向？<br />\n<br />\n黨鐵係成個體制中唯一上巿公司，理論上要跟listing rule, 以我所知佢哋應該無就呢段時間封站就listing rule chapter 14a connected party做disclosure, 如果真係breach咗以我理解係刑事，即係要坐。<br />\n<br />\n點解我會覺得係connected transaction?用家係substantial shareholder (政府）, 而transaction（封站期間只有popo可用黨鐵，in substance包場）亦明顯不是黨鐵日常運作<br />\n<br />\n不過有幾個技術位想大家討論吓<br />\n1. chapter 14a 要求written agreement, 呢個應該真係無，可唔可能apply substance over form?<br />\n2. 個transaction應該nil consideration, 點做size test?（怕佢exempt)<br />\n<br />\n希望大家討論吓，我認識唔算多，如果最後傾到可以一人一信質黨鐵cc SFC, 最少都有阻嚇作用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"966a6b3e11a555eba873e3a2a6ad89085506c65c","tid":1589553,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:41:38.000Z","msg":"[緊急][公投][置頂] 10.1集合定分區搞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589182</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b3bcdf51ef497e8f5ae25ea225f0a50d57e96494","tid":1589553,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:43:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"b5f5066d09a156b90a88418bd645418736f83fef","tid":1589553,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:43:49.000Z","msg":"[一至五帶風向]教大家phone-in節目提高駁入直播室嘅成功率<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587823\" data-auto-link tar